blic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Czech_Republic\"}, {\"begin\": 4347, \"end\": 4352, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Czech_Republic\", \"score\": 0.7566862236693003, \"rank\": 0.321550166602045, \"text\": \"Czech\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Czech_Republic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Czech_Republic\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"PHOTOS\", \"from\": 4239, \"to\": 4245}, {\"ngram\": \"ALPINE PRO, CZECH OLYMPIC COMMITTEE\", \"from\": 4247, \"to\": 4282}, {\"ngram\": \"first glance\", \"from\": 4286, \"to\": 4298}, {\"ngram\": \"Alpine Pro\", \"from\": 4369, \"to\": 4379}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Arguably, the trench coat resembles a stained smock you would put on to protect yourclothes while painting walls.\", \"from\": 4398, \"to\": 4511, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the trench coat\", \"from\": 4408, \"to\": 4423}, {\"ngram\": \"a stained smock\", \"from\": 4434, \"to\": 4449}, {\"ngram\": \"yourclothes\", \"from\": 4478, \"to\": 4489}, {\"ngram\": \"walls\", \"from\": 4505, \"to\": 4510}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But the fit isflattering, and no one can say theoutfitsare boring or forgettable.\", \"from\": 4513, \"to\": 4594, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"But the fit isflattering\", \"from\": 4513, \"to\": 4537}, {\"ngram\": \"no one\", \"from\": 4543, \"to\": 4549}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The inner uniform consists of a more conventional sports T-shirt and a pair of casual trousers.\", \"from\": 4596, \"to\": 4691, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The inner uniform\", \"from\": 4596, \"to\": 4613}, {\"ngram\": \"a more conventional sports T-shirt\", \"from\": 4626, \"to\": 4660}, {\"ngram\": \"a pair\", \"from\": 4665, \"to\": 4671}, {\"ngram\": \"casual trousers\", \"from\": 4675, \"to\": 4690}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Notably, the triangular pattern on the back of the shirt calls to mind the triangle on the Czech flag, which is red, 