ncement) before other news outlets pick this up,\\\" urged another user.\", \"from\": 7434, \"to\": 7543, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"(this announcement\", \"from\": 7463, \"to\": 7481}, {\"ngram\": \"other news outlets\", \"from\": 7490, \"to\": 7508}, {\"ngram\": \"another user\", \"from\": 7530, \"to\": 7542}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The ribbing was savage enough that the Olympic Council went back to the drawing board with official manufacturer Yonex Sunrise.\", \"from\": 7545, \"to\": 7672, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7658, \"end\": 7663, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yonex\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Yonex\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yonex\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yonex\"}, {\"begin\": 7664, \"end\": 7671, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sunrise\", \"score\": 0.9828141054499793, \"rank\": 0.017486414220820454, \"text\": \"Sunrise\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sunrise\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sunrise\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The ribbing\", \"from\": 7545, \"to\": 7556}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Council\", \"from\": 7580, \"to\": 7599}, {\"ngram\": \"the drawing board\", \"from\": 7613, \"to\": 7630}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The updated iteration uses a thicker fabric that does not have the cheap look that plagued the original.\", \"from\": 7674, \"to\": 7778, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The updated iteration\", \"from\": 7674, \"to\": 7695}, {\"ngram\": \"a thicker fabric\", \"from\": 7701, \"to\": 7717}, {\"ngram\": \"the cheap look\", \"from\": 7737, \"to\": 7751}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Meanwhile, the orange collar, cuffs and ombre slash design are subtle but impactful callbacks to the claws of the powerful and dangerous tiger.\", \"from\": 7779, \"to\": 7922, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the orange collar\", \"from\": 7790, \"to\": 7807}, {\"ngram\": \"cuffs\", \"from\": 7809, \"to\": 7814}, {\"ngram\": \"ombre slash design\", \"from\": 7819, \"to\": 7837}, {\"ngram\": \"subtle but impactful callbacks\", \"from\": 7842, \"to\": 7872}, {\"ngram\": \"the claws\", \"from\": 7876, \"to\": 7885}, {\"ngram\": \"the powerful and dangerous tiger\", \"from\": 7889, \"to\": 7921}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The revised uniforms seem to have escaped the ire of Malaysian netizens.\", \"from\": 7924, \"to\": 7996, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7977, \"end\": 7986, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Malaysia\", \"score\": 0.9999999893852874, \"rank\": 1.0037614145124115e-08, \"text\": \"Malaysian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Malaysia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Malaysia\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The revised uniforms\", \"from\": 7924, \"to\": 7944}, {\"ngram\": \"the ire\", \"from\": 7966, \"to\": 7973}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Team USA's uniforms are reminiscent of retro Uncle Sam war propaganda posters, minus the top hats.\", \"from\": 7998, \"to\": 8096, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7998, \"end\": 8006, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.455818921765375e-14, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 8043, \"end\": 8052, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wikipedia\", \"score\": 0.583228676048671, \"rank\": 0.7145933337409283, \"text\": \"Uncle Sam\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wikipedia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wikipedia\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the top hats\", \"from\": 8083, \"to\": 8095}]}, {\"sentence\": \"PHOTOS: RALPH LAUREN You cannot go wrong with a reputable American fashion house like Ralph Lauren designing your Olympics kit, right?\", \"from\": 8098, \"to\": 8233, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8157, \"end\": 8165, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_English\", \"score\": 0.9993481276246583, \"rank\": 0.0006522975905407271, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_English\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_English\"}, {\"begin\": 8185, \"end\": 8197, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ralph_Lauren\", \"score\": 0.9999999691817725, \"rank\": 3.0817937463448996e-08, \"text\": \"Ralph Lauren\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ralph_Lauren\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ralph_Lauren\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"RALPH LAUREN\", \"from\": 8106, \"to\": 8118}, {\"ngram\": \"your Olympics kit\", \"from\": 8207, \"to\": 8224}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After all, it is a celebrity favourite for glamorous red-carpet events and award shows, and during sophisticated sporting events such as the annual Wimbledon tennis tournament in London.\", \"from\": 8234, \"to\": 8420, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8413, \"end\": 8419, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.5394944893655851e-19, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a celebrity favourite\", \"from\": 8251, \"to\": 8272}, {\"ngram\": \"glamorous red-carpet events and award shows\", \"from\": 8277, \"to\": 8320}, {\"ngram\": \"sophisticated sporting events\", \"from\": 8333, \"to\": 8362}, {\"ngram\": \"the annual Wimbledon tennis tournament\", \"from\": 8371, \"to\": 8409}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But that is precisely the problem, as Team USA's uniforms make them look like posh prep school students who got lost on the way to a horse ranch.\", \"from\": 8422, \"to\": 8567, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8460, \"end\": 8468, \"